The paper discusses the vulnerability of CNN-based image forensic tools to adversarial attacks, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also analyzes the transferability of these attacks, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the security implications of these attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR).
